{
	"info": {
		"_postman_id": "b3a7e2c1-9d4f-4a21-8c6e-reservation01",
		"name": "SmartRide - Reservation Service",
		"description": "Tests all reservation-service endpoints.\n\nBASE URL targets the service DIRECTLY (bypasses the gateway/Keycloak auth):\n  http://localhost:8084/smartride_reservation\n\nPREREQUISITES for POST (Create):\n- user-service (8081) running with a valid user matching {{userId}}\n- trajet-service (8082) running with a trajet matching {{trajetId}} whose statut is DISPONIBLE and placesDisponibles >= nombrePassagers\n- RabbitMQ running (the service publishes reservation.created on success)\n\nFLOW: run '1. Create' first — it saves {{reservationId}} into the collection variables, which every other request reuses. Status transitions follow the state machine PENDING -> CONFIRMED -> COMPLETED (or -> CANCELLED), so not every request will succeed back-to-back (e.g. you cannot Cancel an already Completed reservation).",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
	},
	"variable": [
		{ "key": "baseUrl", "value": "http://localhost:8084/smartride_reservation" },
		{ "key": "reservationId", "value": "" },
		{ "key": "userId", "value": "1" },
		{ "key": "driverId", "value": "1" },
		{ "key": "trajetId", "value": "1" },
		{ "key": "status", "value": "PENDING" }
	],
	"item": [
		{
			"name": "1. Create Reservation",
			"event": [
				{
					"listen": "test",
					"script": {
						"type": "text/javascript",
						"exec": [
							"pm.test('Created (201)', () => pm.response.to.have.status(201));",
							"if (pm.response.code === 201) {",
							"  const j = pm.response.json();",
							"  pm.collectionVariables.set('reservationId', j.reservationId);",
							"  console.log('Saved reservationId =', j.reservationId);",
							"}"
						]
					}
				}
			],
			"request": {
				"method": "POST",
				"header": [ { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" } ],
				"body": {
					"mode": "raw",
					"raw": "{\n  \"userId\": {{userId}},\n  \"trajetId\": {{trajetId}},\n  \"nombrePassagers\": 2\n}",
					"options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
				},
				"url": {
					"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/reservations",
					"host": [ "{{baseUrl}}" ],
					"path": [ "api", "reservations" ]
				},
				"description": "Creates a reservation (status PENDING). Validates the user + trajet via Feign, computes prixTotal, sets driverId from the trajet's chauffeurId, and publishes reservation.created. Saves reservationId for the other requests."
			}
		},
		{
			"name": "2. Get All Reservations",
			"event": [
				{
					"listen": "test",
					"script": {
						"type": "text/javascript",
						"exec": [ "pm.test('OK (200)', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));" ]
					}
				}
			],
			"request": {
				"method": "GET",
				"header": [],
				"url": {
					"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/reservations",
					"host": [ "{{baseUrl}}" ],
					"path": [ "api", "reservations" ]
				}
			}
		},
		{
			"name": "3. Get Reservation By Id",
			"event": [
				{
					"listen": "test",
					"script": {
						"type": "text/javascript",
						"exec": [ "pm.test('OK (200)', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));" ]
					}
				}
			],
			"request": {
				"method": "GET",
				"header": [],
				"url": {
					"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/reservations/{{reservationId}}",
					"host": [ "{{baseUrl}}" ],
					"path": [ "api", "reservations", "{{reservationId}}" ]
				}
			}
		},
		{
			"name": "4. Get Reservations By User",
			"event": [
